178,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e70578cf3ae98264cc339400a8b89c4c9888bd47","tid":2509178,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"可以拎靚女身分證<br />\n日本皇軍年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"用下腦啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:38:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>旺角警署淫警作案示意圖</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fQ4JOpYlr3SL25Y9AkCRpSHD1QQ=/261x210/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3SWRKLDKZ2ZAHEKM23C44G647I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfQ4JOpYlr3SL25Y9AkCRpSHD1QQ%3D%2F261x210%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3SWRKLDKZ2ZAHEKM23C44G647I.gif&h=2d0b68bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1)19歲女事主去年11月初前往天水圍警署報失銀包<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/elqkB0PpZw37ew17btMP_mwqzJ8=/261x210/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JELS2LVQY37RPAP3ZX2TFRAHYM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FelqkB0PpZw37ew17btMP_mwqzJ8%3D%2F261x210%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJELS2LVQY37RPAP3ZX2TFRAHYM.gif&h=7025a8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2)被告梁禮仲其後登入警隊電腦系統，取得女事主個人資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XzEgVMDFpOGROVF4VwEF3ZSTTBE=/261x210/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7ACORUYPVL2WI75NSAJ4YIK2LI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXzEgVMDFpOGROVF4VwEF3ZSTTBE%3D%2F261x210%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7ACORUYPVL2WI75NSAJ4YIK2LI.gif&h=597eac10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3)梁禮仲致電女事主，訛稱邀請她到旺角警署助查<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RH7KvCYw2YZd333jTLmyIkmeaIU=/261x210/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SPWQ5ZKX3Q7YIPCJXVUTYKRADY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRH7KvCYw2YZd333jTLmyIkmeaIU%3D%2F261x210%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSPWQ5ZKX3Q7YIPCJXVUTYKRADY.gif&h=f37bd0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4)同年11月24日，被告在旺角警署認人室內強姦女事主<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pciwUdKKgqUDr9liIV3uWvBW0FY=/261x210/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D6UFHK7KZIQO6LKBKPZUDAHTKQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpciwUdKKgqUDr9liIV3uWvBW0FY%3D%2F261x210%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD6UFHK7KZIQO6LKBKPZUDAHTKQ.gif&h=26fbc739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5)女事主向男友訴說受辱經過，即晚同往天水圍警署報案<br />\n資料來源：案情撮要<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20090919/QIEEGFU77TG2ZUKSZMGJGFHJYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20090919%2FQIEEGFU77TG2ZUKSZMGJGFHJYI%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwaQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=fab80ba2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20090919%2FQIEEGFU77TG2ZUKSZMGJGFHJYI%2F&h=7e752c19\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20090919/QIEEGFU77TG2ZUKSZMGJGFHJYI/</a>"}]}